&lt;p>This is a page about tools for analyzing APK files, which are application packages for Android, and how to use them.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="tools">Tools&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="apktool">&lt;strong>Apktool&lt;/strong>&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>A tool for reverse engineering APKs.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="tabs-0" role="tablist">&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link active persistLang-sh"
id="tabs-00-00-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-00-00" role="tab"
onclick="persistLang(&amp;#34;sh&amp;#34;);"
aria-controls="tabs-00-00" aria-selected="false">Arch&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="tab-content" id="tabs-0-content">&lt;div class="tab-pane fade show active"
id="tabs-00-00" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-00-00-tab">
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>paru -S android-apktool
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#999;font-style:italic"># or&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>paru -S android-apktool-git&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;h3 id="dex2jar">&lt;strong>dex2jar&lt;/strong>&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>A tool to convert Android&amp;rsquo;s dex format to Java&amp;rsquo;s class.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="tabs-1" role="tablist">&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link active persistLang-sh"
id="tabs-01-00-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-01-00" role="tab"
onclick="persistLang(&amp;#34;sh&amp;#34;);"
aria-controls="tabs-01-00" aria-selected="false">Arch&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="tab-content" id="tabs-1-content">&lt;div class="tab-pane fade show active"
id="tabs-01-00" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-01-00-tab">
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>paru -S dex2jar
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#999;font-style:italic"># or&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>paru -S dex2jar-git&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;h3 id="jd-cli">&lt;strong>jd-cli&lt;/strong>&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>CLI tool for Java Decompiler.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="tabs-2" role="tablist">&lt;li class="nav-item">
&lt;a class="nav-link active persistLang-sh"
id="tabs-02-00-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-02-00" role="tab"
onclick="persistLang(&amp;#34;sh&amp;#34;);"
aria-controls="tabs-02-00" aria-selected="false">Black Arch&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="tab-content" id="tabs-2-content">&lt;div class="tab-pane fade show active"
id="tabs-02-00" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-02-00-tab">
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>paru -S jd-cli&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;h3 id="jd-gui">&lt;strong>jd-gui&lt;/strong>&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>GUI tool for Java Decompiler.&lt;/p>
